name: penis on face concepts
description:
penis on face

Penis on face, penis on mouth, cheek press, cheek poking, penis between eyes, 2girls, 3girls, 4girls, 5girls

Usage

Trained on 'penis on face, penis on X,' as the kept tags for everything.

  • penis on face: main tag

  • penis on mouth: penis covering mouth

  • cheek press: penis pressing into cheeck

  • cheek poking: penis poking into cheek

  • facejob: penis rubbing against face; works particularly well with 2girls, 3girls, etc...

  • penis between eyes: penis in center of face, this is actually what inspired me to train this

  • 2girls: yep

  • 3girls: tipple yep

  • 4girls: quadruple yep!

  • 5girls: quintuple yep!

  • 6+girls: no. apparently yes? it's just a bit gacha

note

This one works well, but it's kinda hard to control some aspects. I tried something new with this, and the results are promising, but mixed.

modelVersions.name: v3
modelVersions.description:
third version, but first that I'm sharing.

Min SNR gamma 5, and cosine_with_restarts; the results were decent, more training, less burn

I manually tagged things, then used the tagger extensions set to 90%, which turned out ok, but cheek press is kinda hard to control now; I'll probably remove all cheek press tags from my training data, except for the ones with the cheek indentation.

Cheek poking works for that though.
